></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6rN3NRd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JasonM1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A grapefruit? Why?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QotGVUx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BfHeQDD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/QotGVUx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JasonM1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The hardest moments of my life</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pZDoR3g</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CINoB6I.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I had to make a very hard but important decision today.. I had to decide whether or not to keep my husband on life support or to allow him to pass pain-free.. I know he never wanted to be reliant on any breathing tubes or anything of that nature. .. his mother tried to go behind my back and make decisions but I'm the only one who can even have a say.. I understand that this is her child but to dare ask me to keep him on life support because it's hurting her.. didn't even think about how my kids feel or even how I feel .. but the bottom line is it doesn't even matter how anybody feels .. All that matters is what he wanted . And it's eating me up inside but I'm trying to make the right choice.  The choice he would have wanted... it still doesn't even feel real... since Friday I've only slept 2 hours ... I've eaten once.. but I've made sure my kids are emotionally ok and that they had a chance to go in person and say their goodbyes... the nurses told me that I did amazing while I was taking each child one by one back to visit with him .. I told them it's OK to cry.. we're crying because it's hard and sad because we loved him that much ..  I reassured them and told them they could hold his hand and talk to him .. that he could hear them .. they each said what was on their hearts.. and they all even kissed him multiple times.. I swear he knows that they were there.. my daughter even took some pictures of him so she could remember everything which I think is healthy.. but I just I'm doing my best.. I'm worried that my best is t enough ..</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pZDoR3g</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jessag87]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>“Accidentally Decorated” … A.K.A Destroyed.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/sZBT0lE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mhcGfhl.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.youtube.com/shorts/h8wyupOOy5A?feature=share</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sZBT0lE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[pumpkinSpiceIsGross]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Pull up, pull up!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IZTMzf1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IEmxTzm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IZTMzf1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[hoopsnek]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>OC Miku &lt;3</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SklTtrV</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RtnWXyw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Lo1h6aD.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A different outfit than last week, just thought it works <3
